        private static String avoidNumericBegin(String value)
        Helper method for avoiding a numeric first character in package or class names.
        Parameters:
        value - The value to validate.
        Returns:
        If the provided value does not start with a number the value is return unchanged. If it starts with a number a underscore is added as first character.
